cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI. 

The paper focuses on video captioning, which involves computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.CL (Computation and Language) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes a novel task and a new dataset, which involves machine learning and data mining, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.MM (Multimedia) likely sub-categories as well. Finally, the paper uses prior knowledge building to improve the performance of the proposed method, which involves artificial intelligence, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) a possible sub-category.
